OL,3,CForce fined #60,000 after officers
OL,4,Cinjured by petrol bombs
OL,6,FA police force has been fined #60,000
OL,7,Fafter four officers suffered petrol
OL,8,Fbomb burns when a riot training
OL,9,Fexercise went wrong.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,12,FSafety Executive (HSE) found the
OL,13,FDerbyshire Police officers had been
OL,14,Fexposed to "significant and avoidable"
OL,15,Frisks during the exercise in Rotherham.
OL,17,FDerbyshire Constabulary admitted
OL,18,Fhealth and safety breaches at
OL,19,FSheffield Magistrates Court and was
OL,20,Ffined #60,000 with #9,470 costs.
