OL,3,CForce fined #60,000 after officers
OL,4,Cinjured by petrol bombs
OL,6,FFour suffered burns to their lower
OL,7,Fbodies, including three who needed
OL,8,Fhospital treatment.
OL,10,FAll four have since returned to work,
OL,11,Fbut were left with permanent scarring
OL,12,Fand lasting psychological problems.
OL,14,FThe HSE found the force failed to
OL,15,Fproperly plan and risk-assess the
OL,16,Fexercise.
