OL,6,FInsp Elsegood said: "Highrisk
OL,7,Ftraining activities must be planned
OL,8,Fand controlled with the same care and
OL,9,Fprofessionalism expected in any other
OL,10,Fworkplace.
OL,12,F"The risks created by the training
OL,13,Fshould have been identified as part of
OL,14,Fthe constabulary's risk assessments
OL,15,Fand appropriately controlled."
